      • LeafParticle

        public LeafParticle​(org.bukkit.Location loc)
        Creates a new leaf effect. Leaves when ticked will slowly fall until they hit a non passable block or there lifetime has ended.
        Parameters:
        loc - location to spawn the effect at.

      • LeafParticle

        public LeafParticle​(org.bukkit.Location loc,
                    EternalEngine engine)
        Creates a new leaf effect. Leaves when ticked will slowly fall until they hit a non passable block or there lifetime has ended. Using this method will also call the LeafSpawnEvent.
        Parameters:
        loc - location to spawn the effect at.
        engine - engine for the plugin, when this is set wind forces will be applied to the effect.
